# Project Structure Guide

This is an Astro-based project with TypeScript support. Here's the main structure:

## Core Files
- [astro.config.ts](mdc:astro.config.ts) - Main Astro configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies and scripts

## Source Directory (`src/`)
- [src/components/](mdc:src/components/) - Reusable UI components
- [src/layouts/](mdc:src/layouts/) - Page layouts and templates
- [src/pages/](mdc:src/pages/) - Route pages
- [src/content/](mdc:src/content/) - Content collections
- [src/styles/](mdc:src/styles/) - Global styles and CSS
- [src/utils/](mdc:src/utils/) - Utility functions
- [src/types/](mdc:src/types/) - TypeScript type definitions
- [src/i18n.ts](mdc:src/i18n.ts) - Internationalization configuration
- [src/middleware.ts](mdc:src/middleware.ts) - Request middleware

## Configuration
- [uno.config.js](mdc:uno.config.js) - UnoCSS configuration
- [eslint.config.mjs](mdc:eslint.config.mjs) - ESLint configuration
- [mise.toml](mdc:mise.toml) - Development environment configuration

## Documentation
- [README.md](mdc:README.md) - Project documentation
- [README.zh-CN.md](mdc:README.zh-CN.md) - Chinese documentation
